// ============================================================
// The actual global option-value variables (`OptionVars`).
//
// One flat struct mirroring every one of the header's 336 `EXTERN`/
// `extern` option-value variables (excluding `empty_string_option`,
// translated separately above as a plain constant), in the same order,
// with the same terse `///< 'optionname'` comments as the original -
// see `globals.rs`'s own module doc comment for why this crate keeps
// this "one flat process-wide struct" architecture rather than
// splitting into per-subsystem globals or threading an explicit
// parameter through every future translated function.
// ============================================================

